<strong>Superheater</strong>

A block placed against any large <a href="crucible">crucible</a>'s base. Adds <strong>+300°C</strong> to that crucible's temperature ceiling.

<strong>Effect by crucible</strong>
• Steel crucible → reaches mithril temperature.
• Adamantite crucible → reaches runite (the ladder's previously-missing bulk option).
• Dragon crucible → no effect; already at max.

<strong>Does not stack</strong>
The strongest single neighboring superheater counts; a wall of them contributes only one.

<strong>Recipe</strong>
Adamantite plates + rods around a magma scoop.

<strong>In world</strong>
The attached crucible's block-info shows "Superheater attached: +300°C".
